			What is G50?		
				
				
				
			It's Golf coaching redefined		
				
				
				
							G50 creates a more intimate coaching environment for improving player performance, with a mission to enhance learning experiences through small, focused sessions.						
				
				
				
					
			
						
									Learn More
					
					
		
				
				
					
		
					
		
				
				
					
			
		
				
				
					
		
				
			
						
				
					
			
		
				
				
				
				
					
			
		
				
				
					
		
					
		
				
							
							
					
			
							
		
				
			
						
				
					
			
			
			
							
				
									
				
									
			
						
				
									
				
									
			
						
				
									
				
									
			
						
				
									
				
									
			
						
				
									
				
									
			
						
		
				
				
				
				
			Why small group coaching?		
				
				
				
			ITS JUST LIKE PLAYING A ROUND		
				
				
				
							G50 allows you to train with others in a small group format allowing you to feel part of a community.						
				
					
		
				
			
							
		
					
		
				
							
							
					
			
						
						
					
			
						
				
			How does G50 work?		
				
				
				
			IT’S Simple		
				
				
				
							G50 offers innovative, functional small group workouts that are fast, fun and results-driven. Our goal is to help you become the healthiest, strongest and most consistent golfer you can be.						
				
				
				
					
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Drivers
					
					Mastering the driver is key to maximising distance and setting up your game for success off the tee. At G50, we focus on perfecting your driving technique, ensuring you hit longer and straighter.
				
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Long Game
					
					Consistency and precision in the long game are essential to lowering scores. Our long game sessions fine-tune your swing mechanics to improve your approach shots and distance control.
				
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Short Game
					
					The short game is where great rounds are made. G50’s short game sessions focus on chipping, pitching, and finesse shots around the green, helping you save strokes.
				
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Bunkers
					
					Bunker play can be a challenge, but with the right technique, it becomes a strength. Our bunker sessions teach you how to get out of the sand cleanly and with confidence.
				
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Putting
					
					Putting is the most crucial part of scoring well. In our putting sessions, you’ll learn how to read greens better, improve your stroke, and sink more putts under pressure.

			Why g50?		
				
				
				
			Its focused on what you need most, when you need it most and where you need it most		
				
				
				
					
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Skills
					
					G50 provides the opportunity for you to work on what skills you feel you need to work on or refine at any given time. Had a bad day with the driver? Jump into the next Driver session. Lost your confidence around the green? Let’s look at the short game. Golf is a perpetual cycle of improvement so no matter if you are struggling or how well you’re playing, there will always be an area that needs some focus.
				
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Multiple locations
					
					At G50 Golf, we are expanding rapidly across Australia. Currently, we offer small group coaching sessions at select locations on the Sunshine Coast, but we’re not stopping there. Our vision is to bring G50’s tailored, intimate coaching experience to golfers nationwide, ensuring every region has access to our innovative training model. Stay tuned as we continue to add more locations, bringing our expertise to your local course or driving range soon!
				
							
					
													
															
								
														
												PGA Accredited coaches 
					
					At G50 Golf, we pride ourselves on providing the highest quality coaching and training experience. All our golf coaches are fully qualified PGA professionals, ensuring you receive expert guidance on every swing. Additionally, our personal trainers are certified professionals, bringing a wealth of fitness knowledge to help optimise your performance both on and off the course. With G50, you’re always in expert hands.
				
							
					
													
															
								
														
												Sessions
					
					At G50 Golf, we offer a range of specialised sessions tailored to every aspect of your game. From Drivers and Long Game to Short Game, Bunkers, and Putting, we focus on honing your skills with expert instruction. Additionally, we provide Mobility, Strength & Conditioning, and Speed sessions to enhance your overall performance. Whether you’re a beginner, a junior, a lady golfer, or looking to improve in specific areas, G50 has the perfect program for you, tailored to your needs.
				
								
				
				
					
		
					
		
					
		
					
		
				
				
					
						
					
			
						
				
																										
				
				
				
			About G50 Golf		
				
				
				
							G50 Golf provides small group coaching in classes, with no more than 4 players, at your local course or driving range.
